    <mxCell id="26" value="&lt;b&gt;⑩ build_advisor_system_prompt()&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• Role: &quot;Trợ lý Fin&quot; + persona&lt;br/&gt;• route=internal_data&lt;br/&gt;• financial_profile + risk_profile&lt;br/&gt;• calculations (từ bước ⑨)&lt;br/&gt;• tool_context: {structured, unstructured}&lt;br/&gt;• recent_messages: 6 tin nhắn gần nhất"
